      "name": "Zeke the Bartender",
      "description": "",
      "tags": [
        "npc",
        "shopkeeper",
        "zone:station_alpha"
      ],
      "attrs": {
        "description": "A grizzled human with cybernetic eyes and a mechanical left arm. Zeke has\nbeen tending bar on this station longer than most can remember. His face\nis weathered but his eyes are sharp, missing nothing that happens in his\nestablishment.",
